---------------------------------------------------------------------------

mxTidy -- Interface to HTML Tidy (HTML/XML beautifier)

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

IMPORTANT NOTE:
---------------

This package is built around HTML Tidy, a tool for correcting HTML and
XML files freely available on the Internet at:

	http://www.w3.org/People/Raggett/tidy/

HTML Tidy is covered by an MIT style Open Source license.  The Python
interface and the modifications applied to the original HTML Tidy
source code are made available under the eGenix.com Public License.

Here is the complete license notice which applies to the code in the
mxTidy/libtidy subdirectory of the source code distribution:

